org.gearvrf

Class GVRMaterialShaderManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.GVRHybridObject
      • org.gearvrf.GVRBaseShaderManager
        • org.gearvrf.GVRMaterialShaderManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GVRShaderManagers

    public class GVRMaterialShaderManager
extends GVRBaseShaderManager
implements GVRShaderManagers
    Manages custom material shaders, for rendering scene objects. Get the singleton from GVRContext.getMaterialShaderManager(). This class will be deprecated in future releases and there will be no difference between material and post-effect shaders. Now the preferred method of authoring custom shaders is to derive from GVRShaderTemplate.
